text: A person looking at the sky
I'm curling in my sleeping bag
all dressed up in my shower cap
soon I'll be on the largest screen
with my head in a guillotine
My hair smells like an old dishrag
my face looks like a used doormat
my spine is like a horizontal bar
These are just some things you'll find in ImageNet
A thousand cuts of joy but mostly things to pet
and bring them all to my whiskey jug
watch out for the king snake
and don't forget the night snake
and bring them all to my whiskey jug
